27
00:02:10,010 --> 00:02:20,050
[Legend of Awakening]

28
00:02:20,050 --> 00:02:22,740
[Episode 24]

29
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,600
Are you okay?

30
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,840
I am fine.

31
00:02:32,340 --> 00:02:35,619
You just said that you like me,

32
00:02:35,619 --> 00:02:37,999
and you wouldn't hesitate to go through fire and water for me.

33
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,400
Is it true or were you just acting?

34
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:44,440
I'll tell you when this is all over.

35
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:50,539
Boss, can you flirt at another time?

36
00:02:50,539 --> 00:02:52,519
I saw Eldest Senior in the city.

37
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,799
He got into the lodging in disguise.

38
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:57,420
The Mountain and Sea Gang is going to destroy the peace talk

39
00:02:57,420 --> 00:02:59,920
but Qin Qi values the peace talk.

40
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:03,780
Now that Xifan is involved, this issue is getting more troublesome.

41
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:06,770
[Yuezhou Lodging]

42
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:12,660
Xu Tianbing is a general with such a narrow mind.

43
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:15,320
General, why were you so enduring?

44
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:19,659
Xu Tianbing is domineering but he is also the general of Tan.

45
00:03:19,659 --> 00:03:24,060
There must be some issues for his willfulness.

46
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:26,760
Who is that?

47
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,820
I'll send someone to chase after them.

48
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:32,300
Don't make trouble!

49
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:36,020
Go and get our brothers to guard here, I will go and take a look.

50
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:45,600
This is no trivial matter, make no move without careful thought.

51
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:50,060
Mo Lin, you try to distract them for me to go in and find Qin Qi.

52
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:54,399
Boss, I'll handle this, just take care of yourself.

53
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:05,079
Someone come! Catch the thief!

54
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,239
The peeper with his head covered, don't run!

55
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,639
- Come on, catch me!
- Stop, stop!

56
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:11,100
- Stop!
- Stop running!

57
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:15,260
We don't know what's going on inside so I need someone outside.

58
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:18,509
Wait for me here, I will be right back.

59
00:04:18,509 --> 00:04:22,620
Don't worry! I won't let anything happen to your brother.

60
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:24,600
Be careful!

61
00:04:42,710 --> 00:04:51,870
[Peace and Prosperity]

62
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:26,960
Yan Xifan?

63
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:31,439
- What trick are you trying to play?
- General Qin.

64
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:33,879
Even if you are the first general of Shuo,

65
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:36,200
and can use four pneumatic powers,

66
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:39,279
you're no match for me now because you've been poisoned by my needle.

67
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:42,040
I urge you not to do something you will regret.

68
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:48,040
You killed Xu Tianbing.

69
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,600
Now you've hurt me with a hidden weapon.

70
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:55,840
Does the Mountain and Sea Gang really think this will stop the peace talk?

71
00:05:55,840 --> 00:06:00,160
Killing the generals of the two countries will only make us share the same hatred.

72
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:03,800
General Qin, you look down too much on the Mountain and Sea Gang.

73
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,120
I heard that Xu Tianbing had bad temper

74
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:09,000
and that he's argued with you several times before.

75
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,360
It's well known that you two don't get along well.

76
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,760
Try to imagine that!

77
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:18,679
The general of Shuo killed the general of Tan.

78
00:06:18,679 --> 00:06:21,779
So how can you continue the peace talk?

79
00:06:21,779 --> 00:06:25,659
- You're setting me up!
- Exactly! I'm setting you up.

80
00:06:25,659 --> 00:06:29,940
But isn't that what General Qin does best?

81
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:33,100
You hid the identity of the Wen Gecheng before.

82
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:38,679
You set us up for murdering the official and had me on the run this whole way.

83
00:06:38,679 --> 00:06:44,040
Did you ever think that retribution would fall on you so soon?

84
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:49,060
You will bear the name of this eternal sinner.

85
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:53,740
Yan Xifan, I, Qin Qi, as a general of Shuo,

86
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,920
I won't let you win.

87
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:25,220
Lu Ping,

88
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:28,999
you really want to throw your life away by involving yourself in this mess?

89
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:32,499
- You'd better run.
- Lu Ping, what are you going to do?

90
00:07:32,499 --> 00:07:35,020
You are the general of Shuo.

91
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:39,320
I am just a nobody, your life is worthwhile.

92
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:45,340
The things between he and I,

93
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:47,560
we can fix them ourselves.

94
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,999
Assassin! Catch the assassin!

95
00:07:56,999 --> 00:08:00,880
Hurry! Are you still waiting to be caught?

96
00:08:26,220 --> 00:08:28,179
General, what happened?

97
00:08:28,179 --> 00:08:30,400
Let's get out of here first!

98
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:38,400
Don't bother! You can't catch him.

99
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:41,300
Lu Ping, do you really want to fight me?

100
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:44,720
Do Eldest Senior even consider me a brother anymore?

101
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,860
[Peace and Prosperity]

102
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:50,920
Eldest Senior, they are coming.

103
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:53,060
Come with me right now!

104
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:56,060
There's still time for things to change.

105
00:08:56,060 --> 00:09:00,279
You got yourself here so don't blame me for being merciless.

106
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,880
Over there!

107
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:06,260
Go inside.
[Peace and Prosperity]

108
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:27,779
Minister Xia, how do you explain this?

109
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:32,780
Lu Ping? Why are you here?

110
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:34,960
What happened?

111
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:40,559
Minister Xu, he is suspected to be a spy of the Mountain and Sea Gang.

112
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:42,579
He is very cruel.

113
00:09:42,579 --> 00:09:45,920
He had murdered our officials in Shuo.

114
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:48,379
Now, he's killed General Xu.

115
00:09:48,379 --> 00:09:51,840
This… He is extremely audacious.

116
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:55,300
- Guards! Get him!
- Yes.

117
00:09:59,430 --> 00:10:02,860
[Yuezhou Lodging]

118
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:09,219
The boss has been inside for so long; he won't be in trouble, right?

119
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:21,100
There are so many people here all of a sudden, something must have happened.

120
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:24,360
This is no good! I must go inside to have a look.

121
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:40,459
Lu Ping, what happened?

122
00:10:40,459 --> 00:10:42,440
Why have they locked you up?

123
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:45,159
[Yuezhou Lodging]
Miss Qin, it's none of your business.

124
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:47,779
This man is the murderer of General Xu.

125
00:10:47,779 --> 00:10:50,260
Please don't cause our Shuo State any trouble.

126
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:52,840
Killed General Xu?

127
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:59,230
That's impossible! He wouldn't have done that.

128
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:01,140
[Yuezhou Lodging]

129
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:04,419
Lu Ping, what's going on?

130
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:07,200
I promised you that

131
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,640
I wouldn't let anything happen to your brother.

132
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:15,160
Miss Qin, he was caught at the scene.

133
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,720
This is a very important issue.

134
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:19,570
I have to take him to investigate.

135
00:11:19,579 --> 00:11:21,960
- Let's go.
- No way.

136
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:25,480
Sang'er, stop messing around!

137
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,639
- Minister Xu.
- General Qin.

138
00:11:30,639 --> 00:11:33,559
- Where are you going?
- I came back from outside of the city.

139
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:36,940
The general situation has already been reported by subordinates.

140
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:40,160
What does General Qin plan to do next?

141
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:45,440
The murderer, of course, must be severely punished.

142
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:48,919
But I hope that Minister Xu will not affect

143
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:52,420
the peace talk because of any misunderstanding.

144
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:54,779
General Qin has a point.

145
00:11:54,779 --> 00:11:56,939
However, I will still take him with me.

146
00:11:56,939 --> 00:12:01,339
You have my promise! This matter will be handled carefully.
[Yuezhow Lodging]

147
00:12:01,339 --> 00:12:03,060
Please.

148
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:10,260
[Yuezhou Lodging]

149
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,740
Sang'er.

150
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:14,500
Sang'er, it's all part of the Mountain and Sea Gang's plan.

151
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:17,580
Xu Tianbing has high prestige in the army.

152
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:21,540
And I'm a special envoy of Shuo.

153
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:24,000
If I had killed Xu Tianbing,

154
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:27,560
then Tan's army would have mutinied.

155
00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:32,079
The peace talk would be bound to collapse and a war would start.

156
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:36,700
At that time, I could only hide first.

157
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:40,959
Yan Xifan escaped so Lu Ping took the blame for me.

158
00:13:40,959 --> 00:13:46,039
It was to turn this matter from political action to personal resentment.

159
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:48,540
He bought time for Shuo.

160
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,460
It's Lu Ping...

161
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:54,580
It's Lu Ping who solved this puzzle for me.

162
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:03,400
That brat, even the Mountain and Sea Gang has been tricked by him.

163
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:06,479
Miss, don't blame the general.

164
00:14:06,479 --> 00:14:09,580
He did it for our state.

165
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:17,280
Sang'er, what kind of person is Lu Ping?

166
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:22,000
I remembered he was a young man acting on impulse when in Kaifeng.

167
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:26,480
However, his action today really impressed me.

168
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:31,280
He is not like you, Brother.

169
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:33,940
He has no ambition about the country.

170
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:39,160
He is timid sometimes.

171
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,960
He is afraid of pain.

172
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:44,010
But he is responsible.

173
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:46,820
He never flinches when he needs to step forward.

174
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:53,220
I believe that when he asked you to leave,

175
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:56,140
he had already made up his mind.

176
00:14:58,240 --> 00:15:01,940
He is a brave man and I respect him.

177
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:05,880
Brother, is there anything we can do to help him?

178
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:10,500
This matter is well planned and closely linked.

179
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:13,880
The Mountain and Sea Gang must have someone on the inside helping them.

180
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:19,980
Wen Rui, help me investigate someone.

181
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:22,300
Who?

182
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:27,840
When did Xu Tianbing's body get moved into the lodging?

183
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:31,060
Whom did Yan Xifan pretend to be that

184
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:33,840
he could sneak into the lodging without being suspected?

185
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,080
Xu Family.

186
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:10,360
Chief!

187
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:20,660
- Who are they?
- They are from the Agile Dragon Army.

188
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:25,080
It seems that they're already doubting Young Master Xu.

189
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:30,870
[Tingsong Villa]

190
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:33,320
What are you doing with Zhou Youlong?

191
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,820
Didn't Young Lord Yan also come empty handed?

192
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,740
You still dare to insult me?

193
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:42,539
Lu Ping appeared all of sudden and messed up my entire plan.

194
00:16:42,539 --> 00:16:46,560
If I hadn't left in time, Chief would have been the one who's in trouble right now.

195
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:48,520
You couldn't even complete a simple operation.

196
00:16:48,520 --> 00:16:51,559
No idea where Zhou Youlong is right now, do you?

197
00:16:51,559 --> 00:16:55,560
Chief, the Mountain and Sea Gang doesn't need such a loser.

198
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:58,459
How we lost today, I can't bear it.

199
00:16:58,459 --> 00:17:02,060
Why don't I kill him on behalf of our gang?

200
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:04,739
- Chief.
- Enough! Stop it!

201
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:09,190
Even if he deserves to die, it's still not you who gets to kill him.

202
00:17:12,330 --> 00:17:16,670
[Sea and Mountain View]

203
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:18,320
Thank you, Chief.

204
00:17:21,620 --> 00:17:25,760
Xu Weifeng, when you came to us,

205
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:30,520
you should've understood that you have to be useful to the Mountain and Sea Gang.

206
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:32,640
If you are useless,

207
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:36,160
you and even Tan state, to the Mountain and Sea Gang,

208
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:38,980
are not worth mentioning.

209
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:42,219
Chief, it's still not a complete failure.

210
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,440
Xu Tianbing has great prestige in the Tan Army.

211
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:53,040
My father controlled the news of his assassination in order to assist the peace talk to proceed smoothly.

212
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:55,140
But rumors are invisible swords.

213
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:58,940
If I leak the information saying that Lu Ping was instructed by Qin Qi,

214
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:01,240
the army will never forgive them.

215
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:04,880
If there is a mutiny in the army, the country will have to fight whether they want to or not.

216
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:09,080
As for Lu Ping, I'll try to force him admit it.

217
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:10,880
You're dreaming!

218
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:14,460
That junior of mine won't talk so easily.

219
00:18:14,460 --> 00:18:16,690
Young Lord Yan refuses to even try.

220
00:18:16,699 --> 00:18:19,159
Are you afraid that your junior would be suffering?

221
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,700
Up to you!

222
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:28,500
This is your second chance.

223
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:32,520
Remember! You won't have the third chance.

224
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:36,299
I will keep that in mind and will do my best to live up to your trust.

225
00:18:36,299 --> 00:18:39,540
Lu Ping is still useful to us.

226
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:44,260
Bring him to me alive when the war begins.

227
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,860
Yes.

228
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:49,759
Young Master Xu, it's been a day already and several of our brothers are tired.

229
00:18:49,759 --> 00:18:54,079
He still refuses to say a word about Qin Qi.

230
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:56,960
He… He even fell asleep.

231
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:59,660
Senior Xu,

232
00:19:00,980 --> 00:19:04,520
were you sorely disappointed when you learned that it was me

233
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:07,820
and not Qin Qi, who killed him?

234
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,640
- Leave us!
- Yes.

235
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,420
You already knew.

236
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:21,720
Qin Qi was led in by Yan Xifan.

237
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:26,260
In all of Yuezhou, the only one who knows

238
00:19:26,260 --> 00:19:29,420
the relationship among us and had time to act is you.

239
00:19:29,420 --> 00:19:31,930
When Mo Lin told me back then,

240
00:19:32,470 --> 00:19:34,380
I already figured it out.

241
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:38,580
I was just a little bit late.

242
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:43,400
Otherwise, I would've made you lose even worse.

243
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:47,520
I don't understand why you would take the blame for Qin Qi.

244
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:50,160
He showed no mercy to you before.

245
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:52,780
I just don't like the Mountain and Sea Gang.

246
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:56,140
I just want to fight against the Mountain and Sea Gang.

247
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:58,220
Is that okay?

248
00:19:58,220 --> 00:19:59,640
Lu Ping,

249
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:04,800
you're now guilty of a capital offense.

250
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:08,299
Qin Qi can't save you, and Qin Sang is in worse position so she can't save you, either.

251
00:20:08,299 --> 00:20:10,220
The one who can save you,

252
00:20:13,500 --> 00:20:15,120
is only me.

253
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:22,910
I just didn't expect that

254
00:20:22,910 --> 00:20:26,160
you chose to sacrifice yourself to break the game.

255
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:29,000
However, I've actually always respected you quite a bit.

256
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:33,799
My gratitude to you was true in the Seven Martyrs Court and at the gate of Yuezhou.

257
00:20:33,799 --> 00:20:36,580
As long as you're willing to give us the truth,

258
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:39,060
then we can still be friends.

259
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:42,240
Senior Xu,

260
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,800
I was wrong.

261
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:50,200
You are not like Eldest Senior at all.

262
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:55,940
His words bite but he has a soft heart. But you?

263
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:58,880
A complete hypocrite.

264
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:02,740
Right now, you are just like the Mountain and Sea Gang.

265
00:21:02,740 --> 00:21:05,400
Didn't you want to know who the real murderer was?

266
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:08,740
Didn't I already tell you?

267
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,680
It's me.

268
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:17,740
If you want to know other things, just get lost.

269
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,800
How about Su Tang?

270
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:36,420
Don't you care about her?

271
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:38,720
You have the Mountain and Sea Gang supporting you from behind

272
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:43,380
but I am not alone, either.

273
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,380
I promise you!

274
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:53,100
If you even touch one of hair on Su Tang's head,

275
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:57,300
you will die without a burial lace.

276
00:21:58,580 --> 00:22:02,460
Moreover, if you fail this mission,

277
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:06,840
do you think the Mountain and Sea Gang will let you go easily?

278
00:22:08,820 --> 00:22:11,500
Senior Xu, what do you think

279
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:16,500
how I have this ability of being able to suffer a beating?

280
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:20,200
Dealing with demons,

281
00:22:22,420 --> 00:22:24,940
aren't you afraid of getting bitten to death?

282
00:22:32,900 --> 00:22:35,819
We have no further news from those two who were sent to track Xu Weifeng.

283
00:22:35,819 --> 00:22:37,940
They might have been killed.

284
00:22:38,940 --> 00:22:41,340
Looks like there really is something wrong with Xu Weifeng.

285
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:45,779
Now that we know, should we report it to Tan and save Lu Ping?

286
00:22:45,779 --> 00:22:47,060
No way!

287
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:51,580
Oral expressions cannot be taken as evidence.

288
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:55,699
Right now, the peace talk can continue all because Minister Xu has been holding off the news that Xu Tianbing is dead.

289
00:22:55,699 --> 00:22:59,900
However, Xu Weifeng is the son of Xu Yanling so words alone aren't enough for evidence.

290
00:22:59,900 --> 00:23:03,199
If we speak rashly, it will only make Minister Xu look biased.

291
00:23:03,199 --> 00:23:07,199
Right now, only if we can secure the evidence and give it to Tan, then we can control the damage.

292
00:23:07,199 --> 00:23:08,800
General Qin.

293
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:12,019
General Qin, bad news!

294
00:23:12,019 --> 00:23:15,420
Right now, somehow the army has found out that Xu Tianbing is dead.

295
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:18,799
Now, the soldiers are angry and they want to fight.

296
00:23:18,799 --> 00:23:20,640
I really can't control them.

297
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:24,179
General Qin, why are you putting this off?

298
00:23:24,179 --> 00:23:25,740
What do you want, Minister Xia?

299
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:29,339
Lu Ping comes from our country but he is the murderer.

300
00:23:29,339 --> 00:23:32,760
His execution will calm the army.

301
00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:36,340
What do you want to do with his life after all this?

302
00:23:36,340 --> 00:23:39,740
Minister Xia, I have my own opinions on this.

303
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:43,259
The conflict may break out at any moment so what's the point of your opinions?

304
00:23:43,259 --> 00:23:48,040
Do you want to wait until the army mutinies to fight against Shuo?

305
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:15,230
Brother, I already heard everything.

306
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:18,040
Do you really have to kill Lu Ping?

307
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:21,600
Brother, Lu Ping didn't kill anyone.

308
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:25,460
He is a scapegoat for you and for Shuo.

309
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:29,300
Everything is a mess right now.

310
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:31,980
I can only do my best to change the situation for him

311
00:24:31,980 --> 00:24:33,940
but I can't guarantee anything.

312
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:36,760
I don't have the decision making power.

313
00:24:37,700 --> 00:24:40,720
If it gets to the point that you have to choose,

314
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:43,260
will you kill him?

315
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:44,740
Sang'er,...

316
00:24:50,060 --> 00:24:55,520
I had thought that if Lu Ping took the burden of guilt for Shuo,

317
00:24:55,520 --> 00:24:57,740
Shuo would save him.

318
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:02,400
It turns out, none of you care if he lives or dies.

319
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:06,460
Fine! I won't trouble you on this.

320
00:25:07,620 --> 00:25:10,680
If you won't save him, I will.

321
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:14,120
Sang'er, don't do anything rash.

322
00:25:15,420 --> 00:25:18,419
Don't worry! I won't get you involved.

323
00:25:18,419 --> 00:25:21,240
I know that being an official has its restrictions.

324
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:24,160
However, there is still the pugilist world.

325
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:26,440
There must be a way to save Lu Ping.

326
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:45,620
After the spreading news of Xu Tianbing's death,

327
00:25:45,620 --> 00:25:48,740
there is now a conflict on the border.
[Shuo - Tan] (TN: Upside down)

328
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:52,240
My father can't stand the pressure.

329
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:56,100
It's all going according to the plan.

330
00:25:56,720 --> 00:26:00,960
However, why do I always feel like I'm missing something?

331
00:26:01,780 --> 00:26:03,010
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

332
00:26:09,080 --> 00:26:10,700
Bao Niang.

333
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:14,600
- Young Master.
- Go to the lodging to have a look for me

334
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:17,199
to see if Miss Qin has been out these past two days.

335
00:26:17,199 --> 00:26:18,540
Yes.

336
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:20,910
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

337
00:26:20,910 --> 00:26:24,040
Pavilion Master Li, Lu Ping is in danger now.

338
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:26,170
The situation in the state is unpredictable.

339
00:26:26,179 --> 00:26:30,119
Master Yan was hurt by Zhou Youlong and hasn't yet recovered.

340
00:26:30,119 --> 00:26:32,300
Big Dipper, please go to lend a hand.

341
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:36,700
Miss Qin, Lu Ping isn't a disciple of Big Dipper anymore.

342
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:40,520
Why should Big Dipper help?

343
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:46,519
Pavilion Master Li, I'm willing to make amends for Lu Ping's previous trespasses.

344
00:26:46,519 --> 00:26:49,360
However, Lu Ping was also imprisoned for the sake of the country.

345
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:53,140
Is the Big Dipper afraid of power and only seeks self-protection?

346
00:26:54,080 --> 00:26:56,600
The Big Dipper has its own rules.

347
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:01,359
We can't deal with Lu Ping's matter so Miss Qin, please leave and head back down the mountain.

348
00:27:01,359 --> 00:27:04,999
Master, Lu Ping is the son of Master Leng so the Big Dipper shouldn't remain indifferent.

349
00:27:04,999 --> 00:27:08,620
Bai Li, hurry to send Miss Qin down the mountain.

350
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:13,250
Li Yaotian! I can see that you are getting worse and worse.

351
00:27:13,250 --> 00:27:14,940
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

352
00:27:16,060 --> 00:27:17,840
Senior Sister!

353
00:27:19,140 --> 00:27:22,520
The Big Dipper has its own traditions.

354
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:27,059
I didn't expect that the Big Dipper would be no better than a little girl.

355
00:27:27,059 --> 00:27:31,499
It's such a wretched place! Forget about Lu Ping, even I can't stay here anymore.

356
00:27:31,499 --> 00:27:34,400
If they won't go save him, I'll go with you to save him.

357
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:36,880
- Huo Ying.
- Don't worry, Miss Qin!

358
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,790
Our Fifth Institute has already gathered at the gate.

359
00:27:38,799 --> 00:27:42,680
We will go to save Junior Lu with you.

360
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:45,879
Thanks, Elder Chu Min. Thank you very much, Senior Huo Ying.

361
00:27:45,879 --> 00:27:49,159
Wasn't the Fifth Institute grounded? How...?

362
00:27:49,159 --> 00:27:51,700
Who secretly let them out?

363
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:58,039
Guo Youdao died for his disciple so I've let them out.

364
00:27:58,040 --> 00:28:00,039
How can I lose to him?

365
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:02,679
Chu Min, shall we go?

366
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,020
Let's go!

367
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:17,040
You…

368
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:21,559
Master, don't bother! This time, no one can't stop them.

369
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:33,540
Wake up! Stop sleeping.

370
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:36,920
I've been told that today, I have to force you to rat Qin Qi out,

371
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:39,650
even I have to break your hands and feet.

372
00:28:42,560 --> 00:28:46,700
Before you act, please turn your head back.

373
00:28:52,140 --> 00:28:55,219
So dirty! How could you fall asleep in such a place?

374
00:28:55,219 --> 00:28:57,050
Sorry about that!

375
00:28:57,050 --> 00:28:59,920
Who knew at the end of the day, it would be the Fifth Institute who came to save me?

376
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:03,239
Let me tell you! The Fifth Institute was amazing this time. We all came!

377
00:29:03,239 --> 00:29:07,480
Master Chu Min also came, even Miss Qin Sang.

378
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:19,140
- How did you end up like this?
- It was lucky that he didn't die.

379
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:21,920
It's okay. I could withstand the beatings.

380
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:24,440
I won't die.

381
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:28,379
Enough. Stop flirting! We still need to leave here. Let's go.

382
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:43,699
We only thought about how to get in the city but has anyone thought about how to get out?

383
00:29:43,699 --> 00:29:47,519
Why do you talk so much? It's not the first time we've forced the gate open.

384
00:29:47,519 --> 00:29:49,879
There's one word. Fight!

385
00:29:50,740 --> 00:29:53,379
How brave! Master Chu Min is awesome!

386
00:29:53,379 --> 00:29:56,140
- Let's go.
- Go!

387
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:05,020
What happened?

388
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:33,880
Why is the tortoise leader here?

389
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:40,219
Don't think I can't hear you when you speak softly. I have good ears.

390
00:30:40,219 --> 00:30:44,639
You brats, trying to fight with the officials! You're just looking for an early death.

391
00:30:44,639 --> 00:30:48,439
Master is afraid that you would be too reckless so he took me to meet you.

392
00:30:52,080 --> 00:30:54,130
- Pavilion Master.
- Enough!

393
00:30:54,819 --> 00:30:59,780
The disciples of Big Dipper aren't allowed to be bullied by others. Let's go quickly!

394
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,300
Let's go.

395
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:18,900
Li Yaotian, that nosy old man!

396
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:25,800
Now that the Qin Family is involved.

397
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:30,320
This makes it more interesting.

398
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:40,600
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

399
00:31:43,560 --> 00:31:45,120
What's wrong, Lu Ping?

400
00:31:49,690 --> 00:31:53,120
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

401
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:59,440
"From now on, I have nothing to do with the Big Dipper."

402
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:02,140
"From now on, no matter what I do,"

403
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:05,460
"I and the Big Dipper will have no connection whatsoever with each other."

404
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:09,400
These words, this brat had said before he left.

405
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:12,540
Can we just ignore them now?

406
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:17,040
Master, could you save some face for me?

407
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:20,920
What do you take the Big Dippers as?

408
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:24,780
Without the agreement of the master, can you just come

409
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:26,540
and go as you wish?

410
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,410
I previously thought—

411
00:32:28,410 --> 00:32:33,290
Until I say so, you are still the disciple of Big Dipper.

412
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:46,080
Did you really think I've always been scared?

413
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:50,139
Senior Sister, you were right to yell at me.

414
00:32:50,980 --> 00:32:55,039
When I was young, I had a youthful spirit.

415
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:58,740
Now, the longer I live, the less spirit I have.

416
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:03,380
Lu Ping, because of you,

417
00:33:03,380 --> 00:33:05,820
I understand something now.

418
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:10,340
The Big Dipper has a hundred years of history.

419
00:33:10,340 --> 00:33:12,270
There is one and only!

420
00:33:13,120 --> 00:33:16,320
We weren't afraid of anyone before.

421
00:33:16,320 --> 00:33:19,440
We will not be afraid of anyone ever after.

422
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:41,900
Lu Ping, are you willing to regard yourself as part of Big Dipper?

423
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:50,960
Disciple Lu Ping is willing to return to the Big Dipper.

424
00:33:58,500 --> 00:33:59,880
Okay.

425
00:34:02,140 --> 00:34:04,310
All right, all right! we're satisfy now.

426
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:07,210
It was worth it to go into the city.

427
00:34:07,219 --> 00:34:11,069
The Fifth Institute has made great contributions for you have courage and responsibility.

428
00:34:11,069 --> 00:34:14,460
My order! Award the whole institute.

429
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:19,329
Am I dreaming? Us? The Fifth Institute? Awards for the whole institute?

430
00:34:19,329 --> 00:34:21,620
Yes. Yes. Yes. It's true.

431
00:34:24,190 --> 00:34:28,760
What are you still talking about? Drag this brat in.

432
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:30,460
- Let's go.
- Go. Go. Go.

433
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:32,620
- Let's come in.
- Come. Come. Come.

434
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:34,599
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

435
00:34:34,599 --> 00:34:36,700
I can walk by myself.

436
00:34:51,290 --> 00:34:54,500
General Qin, you said there's some doubt in this case.

437
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:57,150
You hope you can find out the truth with time.

438
00:34:57,150 --> 00:35:00,060
I've tried my best to help you in the court.

439
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:02,880
But your younger sister took away the murderer.

440
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:06,519
It's extremely deceiving of you to be so duplicitous.

441
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:09,640
I didn't know of this beforehand.

442
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:11,560
There must be something going on.

443
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:13,899
Your sister joined up with the Big Dippers to break out the murderer.

444
00:35:13,899 --> 00:35:17,360
Our own people witnessed it so what else could be going on?

445
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:20,200
I used to stand for peace.

446
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:23,020
Right now, I can't help but doubt

447
00:35:23,020 --> 00:35:26,640
whether you have other plans for this negotiation.

448
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:31,319
Minister Xu, this is a private act of the Big Dippers and Qin Sang.

449
00:35:31,319 --> 00:35:33,520
Shuo has nothing to do with that.

450
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:38,959
Your sister did that so how are you going to solve it?

451
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:49,920
Minister Xu, please allow me a few more days.

452
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:54,840
I will certainly give you an account of this.

453
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:22,240
[Big Dipper Pavilion]

454
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:28,220
Please give me a pass! I am Qin Qi.

455
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:30,800
I want to meet Pavilion Master Li with something important.

456
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:39,600
Lift your feet.

457
00:36:41,560 --> 00:36:44,200
You are being mysterious.

458
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:46,060
What are you doing?

459
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:48,200
No peeking!

460
00:36:57,080 --> 00:37:00,000
Qin Sang, what are you doing?

461
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:03,779
Lu Ping, you'd better stay here all day and you shouldn't go anywhere.

462
00:37:03,779 --> 00:37:07,660
Why? Is someone coming for me?

463
00:37:07,660 --> 00:37:09,640
From Shuo or Tan?

464
00:37:09,640 --> 00:37:11,500
Open the door!

465
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:19,180
Silly girl!

466
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:31,659
General Qin, you came with soldiers, what do you want?

467
00:37:31,659 --> 00:37:35,119
The Big Dipper has always been independent of the state's affairs.

468
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:38,599
Now you're going to get involved in this mess because of one disciple.

469
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:40,700
I'm afraid there will be endless troubles.

470
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:43,620
How about this, as long as you're willing to hand over Lu Ping.

471
00:37:43,620 --> 00:37:46,800
I will plead on your behalf over the break-in of the prison

472
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:49,320
to keep the Big Dipper safe and sound.

473
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:51,679
How about Lu Ping?

474
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:54,000
How would you deal with him?

475
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:58,180
A war is on the verge of starting.

476
00:37:58,180 --> 00:38:02,540
Only by beheading the murderer in public can we calm Tan's anger.

477
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:05,040
That was for you, wasn't it?

478
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:09,979
General Qin, you'd really use the same trick again.

479
00:38:13,060 --> 00:38:15,859
Brother, you can't take him with you.

480
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:29,959
If it wasn't for your willful and reckless actions to take Lu Ping away,

481
00:38:29,959 --> 00:38:33,500
how could it have turned out like this?

482
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:36,020
If I don't take Lu Ping today,

483
00:38:36,020 --> 00:38:40,579
the two countries will go to war and many more people will die.

484
00:38:40,579 --> 00:38:43,900
Qin Sang, when are you going to understand

485
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:47,640
the responsibility to the people and to the country?

486
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:52,820
- Wen Rui, prepare to search the mountain.
- Wait!

487
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:57,000
Brother, I understand the general principle

488
00:38:57,000 --> 00:39:01,180
but I also know your faith should not be exchanged

489
00:39:01,180 --> 00:39:03,639
for the sacrifice of innocent people.

490
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:07,820
Take Miss away so that she doesn't cause any more trouble!

491
00:39:09,660 --> 00:39:11,480
General Qin,

492
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:17,200
I am willing to go back with you.

493
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:24,220
When I turned myself in at the lodging that day,

494
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:26,680
I was already prepared for the outcome.

495
00:39:26,680 --> 00:39:30,399
I got a few more days so I am satisfied.

496
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:37,160
How could you come out? You can't go with my brother.

497
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:41,120
In the future, don't just lock the door, but also the windows.

498
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:43,260
Lu Ping!

499
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:48,320
Master, isn't Guo Youdao the best at demanding a life for a life.

500
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,860
I am stronger than him.

501
00:39:50,860 --> 00:39:53,460
Lu Ping, you don't have to.

502
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:58,400
You are one of us at the Big Dipper, therefore, the Big Dipper will keep you safe.

503
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:01,540
Since the Wind Takers were destroyed,

504
00:40:01,540 --> 00:40:03,559
I thought I would have no root and no home.

505
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:05,640
That I would wander for the rest of my life.

506
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,559
But I didn't find my place of peace,

507
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:11,960
until master rescued me and brought me to the Big Dipper.

508
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:17,920
So, I won't let the Big Dipper end in the same way.

509
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:32,000
General Qin, I am going with you.

510
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:35,280
Can I talk to your sister before I go?

511
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:01,640
What's wrong?

512
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:07,060
It's just one slap from your brother, why are you so angry?

513
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,759
I am upset with myself.

514
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:13,000
I wanted to save your life but I still cost you your life.

515
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:15,440
Silly girl!

516
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:18,600
You didn't mess up.

517
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:20,880
It's all my own decision.

518
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:24,460
But there's one thing I can't be rest assured of.

519
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:29,100
Now, it seems that I can only entrust it to you.

520
00:41:29,100 --> 00:41:30,900
What is there to entrust? Entrust to who?

521
00:41:30,900 --> 00:41:34,039
What unfinished business do you have? Go and do it yourself!

522
00:41:34,040 --> 00:41:36,540
It's not like I'm saying my last wishes.

523
00:41:36,540 --> 00:41:38,960
I am talking about Su Tang.

524
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:42,359
She is under the control of Xu Weifeng.

525
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:45,540
Find and save her for me.

526
00:41:45,540 --> 00:41:48,539
How about you? What are you going to do?

527
00:41:53,040 --> 00:41:54,760
Don't worry!

528
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:57,460
I am the bandit.

529
00:41:57,460 --> 00:42:00,880
No one's allowed to just take my life.

530
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:03,619
Go and save Su Tang for me

531
