so that I can be more at ease to save myself.

532
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:08,980
Okay?

533
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:11,919
Okay, I promise you.

534
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:23,160
Young Master Lu.

535
