I'd like to go with you to rescue Miss Su Tang.

537
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:33,980
I will do everything I can.

538
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:36,559
Ziyan, you...

539
00:42:39,160 --> 00:42:41,580
You've both have taken care of me.

540
00:42:41,580 --> 00:42:44,260
I regard you as my family.

541
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:47,540
Young Master Lu, if you still regard me as a friend,

542
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:50,480
