543
00:42:50,480 --> 00:42:55,020
That works! The more people, the more assurance.

544
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:58,200
Okay.

545
00:42:58,200 --> 00:43:02,240
Then I entrust Su Tang's life to both of you.

